/*
 * Error Test: E3038 - void function call used as a binary operand
 *
 * Regression for #1483: `1 + nothing()` used to slip through the
 * arithmetic operand type check. Void doesn't make sense anywhere
 * a value does, so the infix-expression resolver now rejects it
 * on either side of any binary operator.
 */

do nothing() {}

do main() {
    mut x int = 1 + nothing()
}
